{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702830/extras/Art_Steam.gif?t=1724077066\" /><br><br>You play as Thraebyn Tarbeard, a young dwarf from the exiled tribes, who is abducted by the vile Oluzhias and forced to do the necromancer's bidding. Along the way, you learn to summon minions to aid you in battle against the fierce and wondrous creatures that inhabit the brutal, untamed swampland, as you quest for the Dhrasmahd\u00f4l, ancient orbs that empower the Yvercrown. Will you help Oluzhias become king? Or will a worthier champion, a mighty Seer perhaps, be the one to finally unite all of the Exiles of Yvermist?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702830/extras/Header1.png?t=1724077066\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702830/extras/Minions_Steam.gif?t=1724077066\" /><br><br>Unlock the power to summon your minions: the skeleton Bhoni, the vicious bone-monster Skrackyl, and the remains of the exiled dragon Dhuma Yhar.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702830/extras/Header2.png?t=1724077066\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702830/extras/Suthyver_Steam.gif?t=1724077066\" /><br><br>Your journey across Yvermist will not be easy. Wild beasts and giant monsters lurk around every corner. Fight alongside your minions and claw your way through the swamp, down the dark hollows, and through the trees of elven Yverwood.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702830/extras/Header3.png?t=1724077066\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702830/extras/Dialogue_Steam.gif?t=1724077066\" /><br><br>As 